{"tid":1702201,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"我一見到女手足被強姦墮胎我個心好似碎咗咁","createTime":"2019-11-09T14:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-10T01:42:53.000Z","uid":316299,"like":184,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"2c012bcec96e937031522f268b8880d9c0c9e7b6","tid":1702201,"uid":316299,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:37:08.000Z","msg":"呢件事係我咁耐以黎最心痛<br />\n可能我自己本身對性好保守<br />\n我係嗰d覺得第一次好撚好撚重要嘅人<br />\n女手足竟然比呢班人渣搞到咁<br />\n我男人老狗都真係想喊<br />\n屌...<br />\n香港人做錯咩<br />\n我求下各位女手足唔好上咁前....<br />\n求下你地<br />\n<br />\n小弟同屋企人關係疏遠 朋友冇幾個<br />\n你地全部都係我屋企人<br />\n我真係好撚心痛呀....<br />\n可能咁講好衰好仆街 但係我感覺係心痛過有手足死.....<br />\n<br />\n三萬黑警上斷頭台呢日 我想親眼見到...."},{"pid":"09154ce269eaeedd5684d035f9d47ca61d3b893d","tid":1702201,"uid":262527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:38:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a91b8c7c02335c9854bd76796e8a1dfdc9c6683","tid":1702201,"uid":8081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:38:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f09e7687a2d9ad95970c1a4710f0943c71c61179","tid":1702201,"uid":316299,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:39:04.000Z","msg":"可能對唔住走左嘅手足...<br />\n但係我心痛過見到手足離開我地<br />\n我都唔知點解...."},{"pid":"a3a2f960b4c02808ea8510d48fcbcbdd52086e97","tid":1702201,"uid":95630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:39:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"003629ff1fe5cb839e94746c42904c4735aa2d1b","tid":1702201,"uid":288678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-09T14:39:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji